results.name: List points (x,y) having integer coordinates, sorted first by radial coordinate r and in case of ties, by polar angle 0 <= phi < 2*Pi in a polar coordinate system. Sequence gives y-coordinates.
comment: Similar to A283308, but with secondary sorting by polar angle.
link: Rainer Rosenthal, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..17664, covering range r <= 75 (terms 0..7844 from Hugo Pfoertner).
